div1.p: IN THE DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON Northern Division.
FILED IN THE U.S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington, NORTHERN DIVISION DEC 29 1916 FRANK L. CROSBY, Clerk, By Edm Laken Deputy
UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON NORTHERN DIVISION
In the Matter of the Application of KUNIJIRO TOGUCHI for a Writ of Habeas Corpus } No. 3482 ORDER DISMISSING WRIT.
IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the Writ be discharged and the petitioner remanded to the custody of the Com- missioner of Immigration.
Jeremiah Neterer United States District Judge
To the entry of the above order the petitioner excepts, and his exception is hereby allowed.
Jeremiah Neterer United States District Judge
IN THE DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON.
In the Matter of the Application of Kunijiro Toguchi for a Writ of Habeas Corpus.
FILED IN THE U.S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington, NORTHERN DIVISION JAN 3 - 1917 FRANK L. CROSBY, Clerk By Edm Laken Deputy
